Package: RSimpleFFI
Version: 1.0.1.9000
Title: Simple Foreign Function Interface using 'S7' and 'libffi'
Description: Simple Foreign Function Interface for 'R' using 'libffi' and 'S7' classes.
    Supports calling 'C' functions with some type conversion.
    Includes standard 'C' types (int8, int16, int32, int64, uint variants), platform
    types (size_t, bool), and floating point types.
